Create a GradeReportTemplateTestType

Source: R/Grading.R
createGradeReportTemplateTestType.Rd

This function creates a GradeReportTemplateTestType

createGradeReportTemplateTestType(
  GradeReportTemplateID = NULL,
  TestType = NULL,
  TestVersion = NULL,
  SortNumber = NULL,
  FieldGUIDTestColumn1 = NULL,
  TestColumnHeaderOverride1 = NULL,
  FieldGUIDTestColumn2 = NULL,
  TestColumnHeaderOverride2 = NULL,
  FieldGUIDTestColumn3 = NULL,
  TestColumnHeaderOverride3 = NULL,
  FieldGUIDTestColumn4 = NULL,
  TestColumnHeaderOverride4 = NULL,
  FieldGUIDTestColumn5 = NULL,
  TestColumnHeaderOverride5 = NULL,
  FieldGUIDTestColumn6 = NULL,
  TestColumnHeaderOverride6 = NULL,
  FieldGUIDTestColumn7 = NULL,
  TestColumnHeaderOverride7 = NULL,
  FieldGUIDTestColumn8 = NULL,
  TestColumnHeaderOverride8 = NULL,
  FieldGUIDTestColumn9 = NULL,
  TestColumnHeaderOverride9 = NULL,
  FieldGUIDTestColumn10 = NULL,
  TestColumnHeaderOverride10 = NULL,
  GradeReportTemplateTestTypeIDClonedFrom = NULL,
  PrintHighestScoreOnly = NULL,
  entityId = 1,
  query = NULL,
  flatten = T,
  returnResponse = F
)

Arguments

entityId

The id of the entity (school). Run listEntities for a list of entities. Defaults to 1 (district).
flatten

Whether to flatten result into a dataframe or return the json object. Default is TRUE (flatten to dataframe).
returnResponse

Whether to return the server response instead of the results. Useful for debugging. Default is FALSE.
fieldNames

The field values to give the created GradeReportTemplateTestType. Each defaults to NULL.

Value

A newly created GradeReportTemplateTestType Skyward's Knowledge Hub
